text: Fritz Gaulhofer (born 25 February 1966) is an Austrian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Austria Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from Weiz District
